{"body":[{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕组 搬运」\n（禁止在B站宣传漫游相关内容，否则拉黑）","location":2,"from":0,"to":5},{"content":"好 到此为止","from":7.33,"location":2,"to":8.81},{"content":"身体强壮了不少啊","from":9.69,"location":2,"to":11.49},{"content":"今天要做些什么","from":13.61,"location":2,"to":15.23},{"content":"对攻吗","from":15.71,"location":2,"to":16.69},{"content":"不 今天做这个","from":17.01,"location":2,"to":19.41},{"content":"这是","from":20.71,"location":2,"to":21.57},{"content":"问得好","from":21.73,"location":2,"to":22.79},{"content":"你闻闻看","from":24.55,"location":2,"to":25.39},{"content":"这些是什么","from":27.39,"location":2,"to":28.73},{"content":"想着和你一起喝","from":29.05,"location":2,"to":30.53},{"content":"我就在森林葡萄的鲜榨汁里加入了蜂蜜酿制而成","from":30.53,"location":2,"to":34.23},{"content":"拿到这些蜂蜜可费劲了","from":34.65,"location":2,"to":36.89},{"content":"怎么了","from":39.27,"location":2,"to":40.23},{"content":"没什么","from":40.65,"location":2,"to":41.25},{"content":"到冬至的时候你也就成人了","from":41.87,"location":2,"to":44.19},{"content":"作为男子汉就必须习惯喝这个","from":44.19,"location":2,"to":46.53},{"content":"玛丽会不会生气啊","from":47.13,"location":2,"to":48.95},{"content":"没事 我们就偷偷喝呗","from":48.95,"location":2,"to":50.95},{"content":"就当作是男人之间的秘密","from":51.17,"location":2,"to":53.65},{"content":"嗯 喝吧","from":55.19,"location":2,"to":56.51},{"content":"好 满上","from":56.97,"location":2,"to":58.75},{"content":"干杯","from":59.57,"location":2,"to":60.55},{"content":"真好喝 真好喝啊","from":63.39,"location":2,"to":66.05},{"content":"没想到会有这么一天 能和你一起喝这个","from":66.09,"location":2,"to":68.69},{"content":"嗯 很好喝","from":70.09,"location":2,"to":71.75},{"content":"照亮前行之路的光","from":73.01,"location":2,"to":77.83},{"content":"在此醒来 本以为是对自己的惩罚","from":83.39,"location":2,"to":90.01},{"content":"那天看到的景色却改变了一切","from":90.01,"location":2,"to":96.03},{"content":"即使看不见未来 被黑暗所吞噬","from":96.83,"location":2,"to":103.63},{"content":"那时候赋予我的东西就在于此","from":103.63,"location":2,"to":110.83},{"content":"仅仅依靠语言是危险的","from":110.95,"location":2,"to":114.29},{"content":"不能光靠力量","from":114.29,"location":2,"to":117.71},{"content":"如果能正视自己站起来","from":117.71,"location":2,"to":121.13},{"content":"就能去战斗","from":121.13,"location":2,"to":124.59},{"content":"渴望生存 祈祷","from":125.21,"location":2,"to":128.93},{"content":"因为曾发誓会去实现","from":128.93,"location":2,"to":132.01},{"content":"所以坚强面对 即使是绝望之路","from":132.01,"location":2,"to":136.33},{"content":"也会继续前行","from":136.33,"location":2,"to":138.75},{"content":"想要守护 重要的东西","from":138.75,"location":2,"to":142.67},{"content":"振作起来","from":142.67,"location":2,"to":145.75},{"content":"不移开视线 不畏惧","from":145.75,"location":2,"to":149.41},{"content":"坚定决心 举起神圣的灯火","from":149.41,"location":2,"to":157.69},{"content":"好 来试试胆子吧","from":164.93,"location":2,"to":166.99},{"content":"试胆子","from":167.79,"location":2,"to":169.13},{"content":"我们去偷看一下玛丽换衣服吧","from":169.13,"location":2,"to":171.73},{"content":"呃 但这不好吧","from":172.03,"location":2,"to":174.29},{"content":"什么","from":174.29,"location":2,"to":175.47},{"content":"-总之跟我来就对了 -走廊 摇摇晃晃的","from":175.51,"location":2,"to":178.19},{"content":"喂 你没事吧","from":178.79,"location":2,"to":180.09},{"content":"没事没事","from":180.09,"location":2,"to":182.09},{"content":"想要偷偷地不被发现简直易如反…","from":192.27,"location":2,"to":196.37},{"content":"慢著 笨蛋","from":196.37,"location":2,"to":197.51},{"content":"呜哇 是谁","from":199.93,"location":2,"to":201.79},{"content":"坏了","from":201.79,"location":2,"to":202.59},{"content":"布拉多 你们在做什么","from":202.59,"location":2,"to":204.77},{"content":"好重的味道","from":204.77,"location":2,"to":205.77},{"content":"你让威尔喝了什么","from":206.11,"location":2,"to":208.19},{"content":"不是 这其实是…","from":208.19,"location":2,"to":210.19},{"content":"我们就是在说要不要偷看一下你换衣服","from":210.19,"location":2,"to":213.11},{"content":"什 什 什么","from":213.11,"location":2,"to":215.27},{"content":"-你们做什么呢 太过分了 -不 我说不要这么做来着","from":215.27,"location":2,"to":219.01},{"content":"我也到变声期了","from":231.61,"location":2,"to":233.45},{"content":"这时候初次梦遗也很正常","from":233.45,"location":2,"to":235.71},{"content":"但居然是因为看了玛丽换衣服才… 怎么会这样","from":235.71,"location":2,"to":238.83},{"content":"威尔你在洗什么","from":238.83,"location":2,"to":239.97},{"content":"呃","from":239.97,"location":2,"to":240.37},{"content":"你手上那是…","from":241.47,"location":2,"to":242.73},{"content":"不准笑","from":243.69,"location":2,"to":244.73},{"content":"以后还是别再喝那么多了 真的…","from":246.47,"location":2,"to":249.67},{"content":"今天就是和布拉多决斗的日子了","from":251.95,"location":2,"to":254.05},{"content":"决斗之后我就要","from":254.45,"location":2,"to":255.83},{"content":"大概春天就得离开这座神殿","from":256.35,"location":2,"to":259.41},{"content":"在和布拉多的决斗中","from":261.23,"location":2,"to":262.57},{"content":"你能不能在不被察觉的情况下 故意输掉呢","from":262.61,"location":2,"to":266.15},{"content":"好","from":268.47,"location":2,"to":269.26},{"content":"威尔","from":269.35,"location":2,"to":270.03},{"content":"我来帮你换衣服吧","from":271.89,"location":2,"to":273.91},{"content":"明天你也成人了呢","from":274.65,"location":2,"to":277.03},{"content":"你决定好要向哪位神明立下誓言了吗","from":277.63,"location":2,"to":280.77},{"content":"这个…嗯","from":281.07,"location":2,"to":282.63},{"content":"大致想好了","from":283.47,"location":2,"to":284.47},{"content":"是吗","from":284.47,"location":2,"to":285.63},{"content":"玛丽 今天我会赢的","from":287.01,"location":2,"to":289.61},{"content":"好","from":292.39,"location":2,"to":292.99},{"content":"伽斯没来…","from":302.49,"location":2,"to":303.43},{"content":"威尔你来了 准备好了吗","from":306.65,"location":2,"to":308.95},{"content":"随时都可以 开始吧","from":309.17,"location":2,"to":311.41},{"content":"好 那就最后再确认一次","from":311.41,"location":2,"to":314.41},{"content":"除了魔法和必杀招式以外 都可以使用","from":314.41,"location":2,"to":318.21},{"content":"出现状况的话 用玛丽的祈祷术来应对","from":318.75,"location":2,"to":321.43},{"content":"一方认输或不能再战斗就算分出胜负","from":321.47,"location":2,"to":324.47},{"content":"小心别丢了性命啊","from":329.31,"location":2,"to":332.23},{"content":"就像暴风雨一样","from":351.05,"location":2,"to":352.57},{"content":"哪怕只被正面攻击到一次就会重伤 无法再战斗","from":352.61,"location":2,"to":355.77},{"content":"哦","from":359.67,"location":2,"to":360.23},{"content":"哈哈哈 你觉得冲到我怀里就有机会吗","from":366.69,"location":2,"to":369.41},{"content":"真是的 才不是呢","from":369.63,"location":2,"to":371.77},{"content":"哦","from":374.21,"location":2,"to":374.95},{"content":"要想完美避开布拉多的一击是非常困难的","from":375.77,"location":2,"to":378.91},{"content":"但如果从正面仅用剑来阻挡的话 剑会断裂","from":378.91,"location":2,"to":382.95},{"content":"要说怎么才能躲过那一击冲过去呢","from":383.45,"location":2,"to":387.35},{"content":"答案只有一个","from":388.51,"location":2,"to":389.79},{"content":"我猜对了","from":391.95,"location":2,"to":392.79},{"content":"威尔","from":403.45,"location":2,"to":404.21},{"content":"居然用肋骨夹住了剑","from":412.89,"location":2,"to":415.33},{"content":"挺不错的嘛","from":416.01,"location":2,"to":418.23},{"content":"我输了","from":418.91,"location":2,"to":420.53},{"content":"哦 不过没有肌肉力量果然很不利啊","from":420.53,"location":2,"to":424.75},{"content":"布拉多","from":424.89,"location":2,"to":425.79},{"content":"呃","from":425.79,"location":2,"to":426.25},{"content":"呃什么呃 你不是说过不再使用那一招了吗","from":426.25,"location":2,"to":430.23},{"content":"哪 哪一招","from":430.23,"location":2,"to":432.35},{"content":"就是用肋骨控制住敌人武器的那招啊","from":432.35,"location":2,"to":435.55},{"content":"可是我现在不就只剩骨架了嘛","from":435.55,"location":2,"to":437.93},{"content":"什么 你那招生前也用过","from":437.93,"location":2,"to":440.53},{"content":"他用过啊 难以置信吧","from":440.53,"location":2,"to":443.45},{"content":"那时候敌人实在太敏捷了","from":443.45,"location":2,"to":446.33},{"content":"而且还直接冲向玛丽 所以不小心就…","from":446.33,"location":2,"to":448.67},{"content":"什么叫不小心就这样啊","from":448.67,"location":2,"to":450.25},{"content":"竟然还能活下来","from":450.67,"location":2,"to":452.41},{"content":"没有祈祷术的话就死定了啊","from":452.41,"location":2,"to":455.53},{"content":"所以就是仗着有你的祈祷术我才这样做的嘛","from":455.53,"location":2,"to":458.59},{"content":"我可是担心得要死 真以为你当场丧命了啊","from":458.59,"location":2,"to":462.97},{"content":"不都跟你说了 不要再用这招了吗","from":462.97,"location":2,"to":464.43},{"content":"-就算是我也懂了 -哎呀抱歉抱歉 不会再用了","from":464.43,"location":2,"to":466.61},{"content":"-你听懂了吗  就是你不许再用了的意思\n-这就是所谓的“两口子吵架用不着劝”吧","from":466.65,"location":2,"to":468.23},{"content":"-知道了知道了 -这就是所谓的“两口子吵架用不着劝”吧","from":468.25,"location":2,"to":469.53},{"content":"威尔","from":470.97,"location":2,"to":471.73},{"content":"虽然没有赢我 但是这样已经很棒了","from":472.01,"location":2,"to":475.57},{"content":"虽然没有赢我","from":476.07,"location":2,"to":477.81},{"content":"用不着说两遍啊","from":477.81,"location":2,"to":479.81},{"content":"下次我一定会赢你","from":479.81,"location":2,"to":481.81},{"content":"哈哈哈 要的就是这种干劲 小威尔","from":481.81,"location":2,"to":485.11},{"content":"好痛","from":485.11,"location":2,"to":486.67},{"content":"别太得意忘形了","from":486.97,"location":2,"to":488.37},{"content":"你们两个都认真一点","from":488.37,"location":2,"to":491.57},{"content":"但是啊","from":491.57,"location":2,"to":493.57},{"content":"我要是有什么必杀技呀秘技呀之类的 能教给你就好了啊","from":493.57,"location":2,"to":496.67},{"content":"没有吗","from":496.71,"location":2,"to":497.47},{"content":"没有啊","from":497.47,"location":2,"to":498.71},{"content":"我们战斗的方式根本不一样","from":499.39,"location":2,"to":502.79},{"content":"我也不想把你打造成另一个我","from":502.79,"location":2,"to":506.39},{"content":"所以对我而言很好用的招数","from":507.13,"location":2,"to":509.05},{"content":"对你而言可不一定好用","from":509.39,"location":2,"to":511.15},{"content":"更重要的是基本功","from":511.73,"location":2,"to":513.19},{"content":"你要让自己过去学过的东西 随时随地都能好好发挥出来","from":513.59,"location":2,"to":516.97},{"content":"我和玛丽","from":517.87,"location":2,"to":518.97},{"content":"已经把最重要的事情全都教给你了啊","from":518.97,"location":2,"to":521.75},{"content":"知道了","from":522.35,"location":2,"to":522.85},{"content":"父亲 母亲","from":525.35,"location":2,"to":527.73},{"content":"哈哈 父亲","from":527.73,"location":2,"to":530.25},{"content":"这么说来 确实很像是那种关系啊","from":530.25,"location":2,"to":532.67},{"content":"好像是的呢","from":532.67,"location":2,"to":534.01},{"content":"虽然没有什么绝招可以教你","from":534.33,"location":2,"to":536.11},{"content":"作为离开父母的证明 这个就给你了","from":536.49,"location":2,"to":539.87},{"content":"我所有魔剑中最强的一把","from":540.25,"location":2,"to":543.55},{"content":"我都没有赢过你 怎么能","from":543.91,"