o":1203.83},{"content":"只要能够掌握将其打破的力量就行了","from":1203.83,"location":2,"to":1207.13},{"content":"就像这样","from":1207.13,"location":2,"to":1208.75},{"content":"于是 才有了现在的我","from":1208.97,"location":2,"to":1211.71},{"content":"接下来 我要前往在大动乱中存活下来的人们的国度","from":1212.83,"location":2,"to":1217.23},{"content":"用三人给我的力量","from":1217.85,"location":2,"to":1220.55},{"content":"总有一天要再回到这里","from":1220.89,"location":2,"to":1223.01},{"content":"带着家人和朋友","from":1223.23,"location":2,"to":1225.01},{"content":"介绍给他们三人","from":1225.15,"location":2,"to":1226.81},{"content":"也可以重建这座城市","from":1227.39,"location":2,"to":1229.53},{"content":"到时候 一定…","from":1229.81,"location":2,"to":1231.43},{"content":"威尔 祝你幸福","from":1231.89,"location":2,"to":1233.71},{"content":"然后不可以忘记 要心存善意 诚心祷告","from":1233.95,"location":2,"to":1236.19},{"content":"你是我最棒的徒弟","from":1237.25,"location":2,"to":1239.27},{"content":"今天的比试从内容上来讲 应该算是我输了","from":1239.67,"location":2,"to":1242.95},{"content":"你这个嚣张又聪明的儿子","from":1243.35,"location":2,"to":1245.43},{"content":"爸爸爱你 要变得更强哦","from":1246.29,"location":2,"to":1248.67},{"content":"虽然时间短暂 但能够和你成为真正的家人","from":1249.13,"location":2,"to":1251.95},{"content":"我真的很幸福","from":1251.97,"location":2,"to":1253.19},{"content":"威尔 我的好孩子","from":1253.81,"location":2,"to":1256.03},{"content":"妈妈爱你","from":1256.85,"location":2,"to":1259.41},{"content":"咦 等一下","from":1259.77,"location":2,"to":1261.75},{"content":"为什么像是","from":1261.75,"location":2,"to":1262.95},{"content":"最后的离别一样…","from":1263.43,"location":2,"to":1265.89},{"content":"告别完了吗 英雄","from":1279.45,"location":2,"to":1281.83},{"content":"嗯","from":1282.29,"location":2,"to":1283.11},{"content":"请吧 我们已经做好觉悟了","from":1283.71,"location":2,"to":1285.93},{"content":"你们总算是“失去了执著”","from":1286.05,"location":2,"to":1288.99},{"content":"按照契约","from":1289.71,"location":2,"to":1291.15},{"content":"现在我就将你们的魂魄收回","from":1291.15,"location":2,"to":1294.47},{"content":"我什么都 做不了","from":1294.51,"location":2,"to":1296.45},{"content":"动不了 为什么","from":1296.45,"location":2,"to":1298.87},{"content":"求求你 身体快动起来","from":1299.65,"location":2,"to":1301.19},{"content":"“破坏”","from":1301.31,"location":2,"to":1302.63},{"content":"这么说来 还剩一个魔法师呢","from":1310.29,"location":2,"to":1313.69},{"content":"威尔啊 带上布拉多和玛丽退下","from":1314.27,"location":2,"to":1317.95},{"content":"哼","from":1318.49,"location":2,"to":1319.11},{"content":"放心吧 由我来解决他","from":1320.15,"location":2,"to":1320.65},{"content":"（第3话 约定之日）\n放心吧 由我来解决他","from":1320.65,"location":2,"to":1323.81},{"content":"（第3话 约定之日）","from":1323.81,"location":2,"to":1324.91},{"content":"控制不住想说的话","from":1338.63,"location":2,"to":1346.41},{"content":"视野边缘逐渐扭曲","from":1348.63,"location":2,"to":1352.48},{"content":"跳动的心是活着的证明","from":1352.5,"location":2,"to":1360.5},{"content":"如果想活在当下","from":1362.5,"location":2,"to":1366.08},{"content":"就连伤痛也能成为慰藉心灵的魔法","from":1366.08,"location":2,"to":1372.58},{"content":"从今往后的世界","from":1372.58,"location":2,"to":1377.3},{"content":"一定","from":1377.32,"location":2,"to":1379.46},{"content":"如你所愿","from":1379.75,"location":2,"to":1382.67},{"content":"高高举起灯火","from":1383.15,"location":2,"to":1386.51},{"content":"为迷失的爱照亮方向吧","from":1386.53,"location":2,"to":1393.27},{"content":"一起度过的岁月便会得以传唱","from":1393.27,"location":2,"to":1400.27},{"content":"我们的爱回归灯火生生不息","from":1400.29,"location":2,"to":1406.53},{"content":"不再与你分开","from":1412.91,"location":2,"to":1414.31},{"content":"(灯火女神)","from":1415.75,"location":2,"to":1419.83}]}